-- Slovenia Opposes EBRD Mercator Sale Involvement, Ministry Says
-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 2011-12-16T12:23:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/slovenia-opposes-ebrd-mercator-sale-involvement-ministry-says.html
Slovenia opposes the European Bank
for Reconstruction and Development’s participation in a
“possible hostile takeover” of retailer Mercator Poslovni
Sistem d.d. by Agrokor d.d., The  Finance Ministry  said in a
statement in Ljubljana today.  The ministry believes the takeover of the supermarket chain
by its Croatian rival would have significant negative
implications for Slovenia’s economy, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  